OL,3,CGuernsey charity seeking land and #1
OL,4,Cmillion to combat homelessness
OL,6,FA charity in Guernsey is seeking land
OL,7,Fand #1 million in an attempt to combat
OL,8,Fhomelessness.
OL,10,FCaritas is proposing a modular housing
OL,11,Fdevelopment as a solution for those
OL,12,Fexperiencing housing insecurity.
OL,14,FIt comes after the States of Guernsey
OL,15,Fpoverty report 2023 revealed that
OL,16,F1.8%, or more than 1,000 islanders,
OL,17,Flack secure housing.
OL,19,FHowever, the charity says the extent
OL,20,Fof the housing crisis could be even
OL,21,Fworse.
