OL,4,Cmillion to combat homelessness
OL,6,FCaritas claims that "many individuals
OL,7,Fare 'sofa surfing' or living in
OL,8,Fmakeshift shelters such as bunkers."
OL,10,FThe organisation says to tackle this,
OL,11,Fit aims to establish a modular housing
OL,12,Fcommunity, consisting of 24 homes to
OL,13,Fprovide accommodation for two years.
OL,15,FComparable modular housing is
OL,16,Fcurrently used by the charity Emmaus
OL,17,Fin the United Kingdom.
