OL,3,CGuernsey charity seeking land and #1
OL,4,Cmillion to combat homelessness
OL,6,FCaritas Chairman, Graham Merfield
OL,7,Fexplains: "We visited a number of
OL,8,Fcharities in the UK and they provide a
OL,9,Fsmall home for an individual with a
OL,10,Fkitchen, bedroom, bathroom area.
OL,12,F"They are built in a factory in the
OL,13,FUK, they would be shipped here and
OL,14,Fthen lowered onto a concrete pad with
OL,15,Fthe utilities so we see it as a cost-
OL,16,Feffective way to help those in need."
