OL,6,FHe highlights that islanders may not
OL,7,Fbe aware of the issue, he says:
OL,8,F"Homelessness is often a hidden issue
OL,9,Fin Guernsey, but it is a reality for
OL,10,Ffar too many.
OL,12,F"The rising cost of living and
OL,13,Fstagnant wages have only exacerbated
OL,14,Fthe problem, making secure housing
OL,15,Funattainable for many.
OL,17,F"Our modular housing project is more
OL,18,Fthan just a shelter; it's about giving
OL,19,Fpeople a safe place to call home, a
OL,20,Fcommunity to belong to, and a chance
OL,21,Fto rebuild their lives with dignity."
